snippet: Christopher J. Dorner, the former Los Angeles police officer sought in the region’s largest manhunt, apparently killed himself as the cabin he was barricaded in caught fire after a shootout with officers, the police said Friday.
abstract: Christopher J Dorner, former Los Angeles police officer sought in region’s largest manhunt, apparently has killed himself as cabin he was barricaded in catches fire after shootout with officers.
lead_paragraph: Christopher J. Dorner, the former Los Angeles police officer sought in the region’s largest manhunt, apparently killed himself as the cabin he was barricaded in caught fire after a shootout with officers, the police said Friday.
